{"tid":55924,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"(new 3DS LL) 求game 推薦","createTime":"2016-12-26T18:41:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-04T01:15:51.000Z","uid":46554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"799648013c0760c38ee16048df347b3d4bed272a","tid":55924,"uid":46554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T18:41:51.000Z","msg":"出面爬咗幾版都搵唔到類似嘅post <br />\n<br />\n是咁的 ，今日入手 new 3DS LL （雖然好遲）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n主要想回味童年回憶 ， 買咗mario bros 2 &amp;卡比 <br />\n但都唔想咁貴只玩舊game <br />\n大家有咩game 推薦/必玩 ？ <br />\n（因為對呢邊面知識太少 ，希望巴絲指教）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇類似biohazard 呢啲活動性咁大嘅game 推薦 ？ （biohazard 又賣緊幾錢 ？）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為mario 同卡比都係行前行後咁 ，想玩啲活動空間大嘅game。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n謝謝大家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a3e16c74f8bd045308784c56ddbeb166a08d6a5","tid":55924,"uid":46554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T18:46:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe537b7cc2a598fe8908e60a83a7fa55a9558eb4","tid":55924,"uid":64058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T18:49:44.000Z","msg":"bio hazard revelation 日ver. 但有ENG 字幕<br />\n<br />\nMARIO 3D, <br />\n<br />\n機戰"},{"pid":"bf47fe01ac39d3c7c8f9a2abc61a9c97a7b116f9","tid":55924,"uid":46554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T19:06:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>bio hazard revelation 日ver. 但有ENG 字幕<br />\n<br />\nMARIO 3D, <br />\n<br />\n機戰</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nBiohazard 知唔知大約幾錢 ？ 好似有分兩種game <br />\n有冇全名 ？ 定直接同佢講話biohazard revelation 就得 ？ <br />\n聽日去買先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nMario 3D 暫時唔買住。玩爆mario bro 先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fd0649f587f0b8b04b143e1870ecddb32b4b9c0","tid":55924,"uid":46554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T04:59:46.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"36d4cb07b57aaa32422e43e41004b8ae2d8729f9","tid":55924,"uid":46554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T05:00:00.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"05516285c0fb9b8eb7f3f75d27c4c4209d4bd356","tid":55924,"uid":46554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T05:00:10.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"703dc37adb789891fb1fc593329c4987b13e57a8","tid":55924,"uid":36509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T11:48:41.000Z","msg":"動物之森"},{"pid":"9c344dddf29423e06099df114013b816ed9c5f6e","tid":55924,"uid":36509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T11:50:13.000Z","msg":"童年回憶 - <br />\nPokemon/MarioKart囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30ea1694a33a38a3a5977cbdee34cd5247c814d5","tid":55924,"uid":36509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T11:51:12.000Z","msg":"講下想玩咩類game會易啲幫你諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n動作?音樂?休閒?"},{"pid":"97d05783be373b5cf413d0ec9c4146b08a497a6f","tid":55924,"uid":6324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T13:47:42.000Z","msg":"而家買部new 3ds ll要幾錢"},{"pid":"0b1e25207b67a826c1a89746c3f6559b374064ac","tid":55924,"uid":46554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T15:02:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>童年回憶 - <br />\nPokemon/MarioKart囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nPok&eacute;mon <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\nMario 系列都會慢慢再買。"},{"pid":"7fb80ba1d8cd79e9a48e0c0a3c68869ea1467a67","tid":55924,"uid":46554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T15:02:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講下想玩咩類game會易啲幫你諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n動作?音樂?休閒?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n動作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96c5129a244509b8aedf44adaaca9e2350505826","tid":55924,"uid":46554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T15:02:39.000Z","msg":"高畫質"},{"pid":"e07361fdc9fc4a2f72a67d635795857e2e402b3f","tid":55924,"uid":46554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T15:05:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家買部new 3ds ll要幾錢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇咩色。我無去旺角格價。<br />\n舊色就1190-1300。我綠黑就1400 （16年出）<br />\n我知我買貴咗 ，但懶得出旺角所以由佢。<br />\n如果巴打有興趣出旺角買應該1100-1200都有（舊色）。<br />\n特別版街見就1500-1600。但旺角應該1400-1500都有。有心機就格下價喇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57ae6073055b0397cc199b8cac05ef8b09331bb8","tid":55924,"uid":46554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T15:07:09.000Z","msg":"今日搵咗幾間終於搵到biohazard（12年出搵到都好好運）。想搵多個類似bio 嘅game 重點係活動性夠大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e5ff0788e6e59494461f05b5ca40d5aec46b7f7","tid":55924,"uid":36509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T16:21:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>高畫質</blockquote><br />\n高畫質+動作<br />\nLuigi's Mansion 2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nmon hunt<br />\nex troopers<br />\nzelda無雙<br />\n<br />\n如果日式RPG啱心水強烈建議<br />\nBravely Default (第一集) 同<br />\nBravely Second (第二集)"},{"pid":"a10583f338bd6675190389d171b599abe98c2f66","tid":55924,"uid":36509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T16:25:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>童年回憶 - <br />\nPokemon/MarioKart囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nPok&eacute;mon <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\nMario 系列都會慢慢再買。</blockquote><br />\nMario系列有<br />\nNSMB2<br />\nMario 3D land <br />\nMario Maker<br />\nMario Kart 7 <br />\n值得買<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外唔知<br />\nFantasy Life &amp;大亂鬥啱唔啱你心水"},{"pid":"4bd77fd68984e22f18de2879e84b961981fe1cd9","tid":55924,"uid":36509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T16:37:54.000Z","msg":"呀, 仲有Zelda系列 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nA Link Between Worlds <br />\nMajora's Mask 3D<br />\nOcarina of Time 3D"},{"pid":"e220b3f42fa5667dcdd2c7b744487ba8866c1b8c","tid":55924,"uid":46554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T01:32:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>高畫質</blockquote><br />\n高畫質+動作<br />\nLuigi's Mansion 2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nmon hunt<br />\nex troopers<br />\nzelda無雙<br />\n<br />\n如果日式RPG啱心水強烈建議<br />\nBravely Default (第一集) 同<br />\nBravely Second (第二集)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n謝謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我會去搵下"},{"pid":"f4972a9f5212fce30671c83424d6835aa8d5bece","tid":55924,"uid":11880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T02:02:14.000Z","msg":"芒亨高畫質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ebd143d38b394a9b0465b051bc45c4d1d4673f6","tid":55924,"uid":6324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T02:47:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>而家買部new 3ds ll要幾錢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇咩色。我無去旺角格價。<br />\n舊色就1190-1300。我綠黑就1400 （16年出）<br />\n我知我買貴咗 ，但懶得出旺角所以由佢。<br />\n如果巴打有興趣出旺角買應該1100-1200都有（舊色）。<br />\n特別版街見就1500-1600。但旺角應該1400-1500都有。有心機就格下價喇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我主要玩孖寶兄弟<br />\n2ds夠玩丫<br />\n<br />\n定有勁買勁好？"},{"pid":"3e9d802dc7016d0c63fb608bfeffb9074aa7b775","tid":55924,"uid":6324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T06:22:59.000Z","msg":"頭先在屯門置樂問左<br />\n<br />\n日版機<br />\nNew 3ds ll<br />\n1340<br />\n<br />\n2ds就750<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n價錢正常嗎？<br />\n一隻孖寶280左右<br />\n<br />\n其實有冇話買日版定美版好？<br />\n在香港邊款好d？"},{"pid":"a9e63e5ceaddad60b6f13700605a0484537eae7a","tid":55924,"uid":36509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T07:45:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>芒亨高畫質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n3DS 高畫質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0d996766b8a95d896ad30be42ed73835a27e481","tid":55924,"uid":36509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T07:45:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>高畫質</blockquote><br />\n高畫質+動作<br />\nLuigi's Mansion 2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nmon hunt<br />\nex troopers<br />\nzelda無雙<br />\n<br />\n如果日式RPG啱心水強烈建議<br />\nBravely Default (第一集) 同<br />\nBravely Second (第二集)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n謝謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我會去搵下</blockquote><br />\n最緊要都係search下隻game玩乜,自己啱唔啱玩先"},{"pid":"49d9fb5ce7f5719db3e52776092ddb09e0bacd6b","tid":55924,"uid":36509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T07:46:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>頭先在屯門置樂問左<br />\n<br />\n日版機<br />\nNew 3ds ll<br />\n1340<br />\n<br />\n2ds就750<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n價錢正常嗎？<br />\n一隻孖寶280左右<br />\n<br />\n其實有冇話買日版定美版好？<br />\n在香港邊款好d？</blockquote><br />\n日版 日文<br />\n美版 英文<br />\n港版 &lt;- 唔好諗, 伏"},{"pid":"1c8c667e0df1cac792d25172f963d656e2c6e644","tid":55924,"uid":11880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T07:47:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>芒亨高畫質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n3DS 高畫質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n隻芒亨story就真係高畫質神作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6e78d90cb0a46a6f4eadf11e333b01979fb71b7","tid":55924,"uid":46554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T07:48:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>頭先在屯門置樂問左<br />\n<br />\n日版機<br />\nNew 3ds ll<br />\n1340<br />\n<br />\n2ds就750<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n價錢正常嗎？<br />\n一隻孖寶280左右<br />\n<br />\n其實有冇話買日版定美版好？<br />\n在香港邊款好d？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我就日版。因為有地區限制 ，日版只可玩日版game。XL版只可玩XL GAME。日版就出game 多同快。行貨好多得啲收歡迎嘅game。無物點得簡game玩。又要等出咗日版半年至一年先會出其他版。所以 ⋯ 簡日版會多選擇啲。<br />\n<br />\n但行貨啲game 就平好多 （要散貨） <br />\nEg biohazard 行貨98$ 日貨230$"},{"pid":"8104f0ec1f3b188325ef27f6e5286f2da42ebe8c","tid":55924,"uid":46554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T07:49:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>芒亨高畫質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n3DS 高畫質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n隻芒亨story就真係高畫質神作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n過來人  ？ 好無玩 ？"},{"pid":"5c19d8f9fb879e42a81e6076ded0323792794747","tid":55924,"uid":11880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T07:51:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>芒亨高畫質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n3DS 高畫質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n隻芒亨story就真係高畫質神作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n過來人  ？ 好無玩 ？</blockquote><br />\n育成RPG黎計好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"669350a8b723644a3effb81fa02b52bf4ff6419b","tid":55924,"uid":46554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T08:02:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n隻芒亨story就真係高畫質神作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n過來人  ？ 